Package sorcer.core.provider.exertmonitor.db

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SessionDatabase
    SessionDatabase defines the storage containers for the ExertMonitor database.
    SessionDatabaseViews
    SessionDatabaseViews defines the data bindings and collection views for the session database.
    SessionDatabaseViews.SessionBinding
    SessionBinding is used to bind the stored key/data entry pair to a combined data object (entity).
